Enter your vote today!  A new poll has been created for the 
junit group:

In your opinion, is Test Driven 
Development(test then code) more, 
equally, or less effective than 
traditional software development 
practices for increasing productivity, 
which is, decreasing the amount of time 
it takes to release software products? 

  o More Effective 
  o Equally Effective 
  o Less Effective 
  o Not Sure 
  o Unfamiliar with TDD 


To vote, please visit the following web page:

http://groups.yahoo.com/group/junit/surveys?id=1039817  

Note: Please do not reply to this message. Poll votes are 
not collected via email. To vote, you must go to the Yahoo! Groups 
web site listed above.

Thanks!
